/***************************************************
==================== JS INDEX ======================
****************************************************
// Data js
// Sidebar Navigation
// Sticky Header
// Hamburger Menu
// Scroll To Section
// OnePage Active Class
// Nice Select
// ALL Popup
// Preloader
// Sidebar Hover BG Color
// Services Hover BG
// Portfolio Filter BG Color
